  "reviews": "\u201cThe Padre is animated using a voxel art style, aiming to give the game a blocky, surreal appearance as players face down quivering creatures and presences that will whittle down the mind.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.siliconera.com/2017/10/25/horror-game-padre-explores-moments-demon-hunting-priests-suicide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Siliconera</a><br><br>\u201cA fabulously freaky voxel based point and click survival horror with a healthy dose of dark humor.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.alphabetagamer.com/the-padre-alpha-download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Alpha Beta Gamer</a><br><br>\u201cA voxel tribute to the old horror adventure games\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://indiewatch.net/2018/01/14/padre-game-voxel-tribute-old-horror-adventure-games\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >IndieWatch</a><br>",
